stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft
    Draft --> Pending : submit
    Pending --> Approved : approve
    Pending --> Rejected : reject
    Approved --> Published : publish
    Rejected --> Draft : revise
    Published --> Archived : archive
    Archived --> [*]

    Note right of Rejected
        Error path —
        returns to Draft
    End note
